  "description": "How to appeal a penalty if you’re a company director or an accountant who has received a penalty from Companies House for filing your company accounts late. \r\n",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>Use this service to appeal a penalty from Companies House for filing a company’s annual accounts late.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You should <a href=\"/pay-a-penalty-for-filing-company-accounts-late\">pay the late filing penalty</a> even if you want to appeal, unless there are exceptional reasons, such as a fire destroying records.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"before-you-start\">Before you start</h2>\n\n<p>You’ll need:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the company number</li>\n  <li>the penalty reference</li>\n  <li>the reason for the appeal</li>\n  <li>any documents that support the appeal</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Any documents you upload, such as a doctor’s note or an insurance claim, must include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the full name of the person or company affected</li>\n  <li>any relevant dates</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The maximum file size for each document is 4MB.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"start-your-appeal\">Start your appeal</h2>\n\n<p>It can take up to 30 minutes to apply. You’ll be signed out after 60 minutes if you pause your application and your answers will not be saved.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can only appeal once against a penalty notice.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p><a class=\"gem-c-button govuk-button govuk-button--start\" role=\"button\" data-module=\"govuk-button\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://find-and-update.company-information.service.gov.uk/appeal-a-penalty/penalty-reference\"><span> Start now </span><svg class=\"govuk-button__start-icon govuk-!-display-none-print\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17.5\" height=\"19\" viewbox=\"0 0 33 40\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z\"></path></svg></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/government/publications/late-filing-penalties/late-filing-penalties\">Read the guidance on late filing penalties.</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"after-you-appeal\">After you appeal</h2>\n\n<p>Wait for Companies House to contact you with their decision.</p>\n\n<p>If you have not paid the penalty, you may be contacted by a debt recovery agency or solicitors asking for payment. Reply to them explaining you have appealed the penalty.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"other-ways-to-appeal\">Other ways to appeal</h2>\n\n<p>You can also appeal a penalty by email or post.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"appeal-by-email\">Appeal by email</h3>\n\n<p>Send your email with any supporting evidence attached to Companies House.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Companies House enquiries <br>\n<a href=\"mailto:enquiries@companieshouse.gov.uk\">enquiries@companieshouse.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3 id=\"appeal-by-post\">Appeal by post</h3>\n\n<p>Send your letter and any supporting evidence to Companies House.</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nLate filing penalties\n<br>PO Box 710\n<br>Crown Way\n<br>Cardiff\n<br>CF14 3UZ\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"if-you-cannot-appeal-by-email-or-post\">If you cannot appeal by email or post</h3>\n\n<p>You can phone Companies House if you cannot appeal by email or post.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Telephone: 0303 1234 500 <br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 6pm <br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
